               <lb facs="#facs_74_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>Where is this reality alive? It is alive in family, in the social surincundings, and in the church.
               <lb facs="#facs_74_tr_1_tl_4" n="N004"/>Religion education means introduching the child into all three of these realities. And if I say "the child
